BLE and the Update that Simplified the Flight Controlling Mechanic the Most, v10 is meant to finalize the heavy game development for a month or two, however, fixes and improvements will still come if there are any needs for it. this Update adds Controller SUPPORT!!! basically the rest is self explanatory, the update also fixes a bug that due to the collider removal and raycast to prevent going through mesh, even if the Earth's Mesh was not visible in Space, it was still there, so the raycast stopped Player Movement when trying to go down, this was Fortunately FIXED!,\n\nv10.2: the Controllers are now Able to Type on Keyboard to Search and Teleport to a specific Place on Earth, and fixed a bug where the space bar touch collider was small,\n\nv10.3: when you pressed on some specific ui buttons, the code gave an error and every other ui stopped working since they had the same script. this was fixed. 3d Earth Generation to have better quality and faster performance, also loading faster and in larger quantity, we'll have to know if that's the case, if not we'll have to redo the changes in v10.4 :/, another improvement was that flight speed adjustment based on altitude was not efficient, and sometimes caused teleporting instead of flying smoothly, fixed !\nhttps://youtu.be/6s-jkai4_mA\n---------------------", "short_description": "geography teaching hand tracking passthrough VR app/game on Quest 2 Quest Pro, and Quest 3"}]}, "developer_name": "Bowie/Electrum", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rfelQCihEG-gjgHBpxfy5Kd52Y2-Vj9LTwpGWsoWFZ0/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1vkc-TWH53X4qPwdf9J-erq8Pl_xvB_sYFUK2jHG94TY/edit?usp=sharing", "publisher_name": "Bowie/Electrum", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1ZXJHOoHOgvJ6mK5_gHPoqyyQy8B6IKGn?usp=drive_link", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "726368587961803"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1703886060119133"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 4, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1197247534802870"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1218595455967648"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "966363545148360"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "865031525282969"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1197247534802870"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1722030957, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1197247534802870"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8483328601796798", "version": "3902"}, "id": "997411404840848", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8483328601796798"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "v39 is RELEASED !\n\nThis took a few years off my life, for sure.\n\nI was honestly not expecting to work HARDER than I did in the recent updates SO SOON, but here you go, with or without breaking records.\n\n# Introducing Google Outer Space View\n\nYou can now explore the International Space Station while in Space !\n\nAnd yeah, all in 8k !\n\n# Additional\n\n- Small adjustments to make Hand Tracking Flight potentially more responsive\n- Discovered and solved some bugs\n\nLet me know if there are any issues, big OR small\n( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1732316179, "id": "8483328601796798", "version": "3902", "version_code": 3902, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8483328601796798"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "v39 is RELEASED !\n\nThis took a few years off my life, for sure.\n\nI was honestly not expecting to work HARDER than I did in the recent updates SO SOON, but here you go, with or without breaking records.\n\n# Introducing Google Outer Space View\n\nYou can now explore the International Space Station while in Space !\n\nAnd yeah, all in 8k !\n\n# Additional\n\n- Small adjustments to make Hand Tracking Flight potentially more responsive\n- Discovered and solved some bugs\n\nLet me know if there are any issues, big OR small\n( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1732302889, "id": "8482492671880391", "version": "3900", "version_code": 3900, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8483328601796798"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "v38 is LIVE !\n\nThis update isn't small, but a big part of it is into the small things, optimizing for maximum performance, ensuring everything offers the most possible utility, refining UI elements for clarity and design, and improving tiny but important aspects overall.\n\nImmersive Mode Upgrades\n\n- Realistic Night Sky:\nRealistic & natural star fields, long exposure mechanic ( star trails ) for fast Sky Speeds + more...\n- More 'Sky Rotation Speed' control accuracy;\n\nBeautiful new Soundtrack\nListen here: https://youtu.be/7rcSd54dU68\n\nLet me know if there are any issues ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1731873796, "id": "8454094771386848", "version": "3802", "version_code": 3802, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8483328601796798"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "v38 is OUT !\n\nThis update isn't small, but a big part of it is into the small things, optimizing for maximum performance, ensuring everything offers the most possible utility, refining UI elements for clarity and design, and improving tiny but important aspects overall.\n\nImmersive Mode Upgrades\n\n- Realistic Night Sky:\nRealistic & natural star fields, long exposure mechanic ( star trails ) for fast Sky Speeds + more...\n- More 'Sky Rotation Speed' control accuracy;\n\nBeautiful new Soundtrack\nListen here: https://youtu.be/7rcSd54dU68\n\nLet me know if there are any issues ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1731753187, "id": "8446756702120655", "version": "3801", "version_code": 3801, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6320120764784270", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8483328601796798"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "997411404840848"}]}, "change_log": "v38 is OUT !\n\nThis update isn't small, but a big part of it is into the small things, optimizing for maximum performance, ensuring everything offers the most possible utility, refining UI elements for clarity and design, and improving tiny but important aspects overall.\n\nImmersive Mode Upgrades\n\n- Realistic Night Sky:\nRealistic & natural star fields, long exposure mechanic ( star trails ) for fast Sky Speeds and more...\n- More 'Sky Rotation Speed' control accuracy;\n\n( video )\n\nBeautiful new Soundtrack\nListen here: https://youtu.be/7rcSd54dU68\n\nLet me know if there are any issues ( contact.earthquest.site )", "created_date": 1731646253, "id": "8440050236124635", "version": "3800", "version_code": 3800, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}